msgid "# Hunyuan-A13B-Instruct"
msgstr "# Hunyuan-A13B-Instruct"

msgid "## Introduction"
msgstr "## 简介"

msgid ""
"Hunyuan-A13B-Instruct is a fine-grained hybrid expert model (MoE) developed "
"by Tencent. This model has a total of 80 billion parameters, 13 billion "
"activation parameters, supports 256K ultra-long contexts, and possesses "
"native thought chain (CoT) reasoning capabilities."
msgstr ""
"Hunyuan-A13B-Instruct "
"是腾讯开发的一款细粒度混合专家模型（MoE）。该模型总参数量达800亿，激活参数量为130亿，支持256K超长上下文，并具备原生思维链（CoT）推理能力。"

msgid "## Environment Preparation"
msgstr "## 环境准备"

msgid "### Model Weight"
msgstr "### 模型权重"

msgid ""
"- `Hunyuan-A13B-Instruct`(BF16 version): [Download model "
"weight](https://www.modelscope.cn/models/Tencent-"
"Hunyuan/Hunyuan-A13B-Instruct)."
msgstr ""
"- "
"`Hunyuan-A13B-Instruct`（BF16版本）：[下载模型权重](https://www.modelscope.cn/models/Tencent-"
"Hunyuan/Hunyuan-A13B-Instruct)。"

msgid ""
"It is recommended to download the model weight to the shared directory of "
"multiple nodes, such as `/root/.cache/`"
msgstr "建议将模型权重下载到多节点共享目录中，例如 `/root/.cache/`"

msgid "### Installation"
msgstr "### 安装"

msgid "Run docker container:"
msgstr "运行 Docker 容器："

msgid "Build from source:"
msgstr "从源码构建："

msgid ""
"### Software Stack Version Verification\n"
" <!-- TODO: update to Python 3.12 after verification -->\n"
"The environment is based on CANN built into the GiteeAI platform, and successfully runs vLLM {{ vllm_ascend_version }}, and vLLM-Ascend:{{ vllm_ascend_version }} through the Python 3.11.6 Conda environment."
msgstr ""
"### 软件栈版本验证\n"
" <!-- TODO: 验证后更新至 Python 3.12 -->\n"
"环境基于 GiteeAI 平台内置的 CANN，并通过 Python 3.11.6 Conda 环境成功运行 vLLM {{ vllm_ascend_version }} 和 vLLM-Ascend:{{ vllm_ascend_version }}。"

msgid "## Deployment"
msgstr "## 部署"

msgid "### Single-node Deployment (4-NPU)"
msgstr "### 单节点部署（4-NPU）"

msgid "### Key Performance Indicators"
msgstr "### 关键性能指标"

msgid "Based on verified CANN 8.5.1 test logs:"
msgstr "基于已验证的 CANN 8.5.1 测试日志："

msgid ""
"- Memory usage for weights: each NPU has a static memory usage of approximately 37.46 GB.\n"
"- Graph compilation (ACL Graph): with PIECEWISE mode enabled, the system automatically captures the graph in approximately 18 seconds, which can significantly accelerate subsequent inference.\n"
"- KV cache capacity: the remaining NPU memory can provide concurrent cache space for approximately 529,152 tokens."
msgstr ""
"- 权重内存占用：每个 NPU 的静态内存占用约为 37.46 GB。\n"
"- 图编译（ACL Graph）：启用 PIECEWISE 模式后，系统约在 18 秒内自动捕获计算图，可显著加速后续推理。\n"
"- KV 缓存容量：剩余 NPU 内存可为约 529,152 个 token 提供并发缓存空间。"

msgid "## Functional Verification"
msgstr "## 功能验证"

msgid "Expected output:"
msgstr "预期输出："

msgid "## Accuracy Evaluation"
msgstr "## 精度评估"

msgid ""
"On the GiteeAI platform, the model was tested and verified using the "
"AISBench tool on the GSM8K benchmark set: Under the 7cd45e version "
"configuration, the model achieved an accuracy of 94.77% in the accuracy "
"generation mode."
msgstr ""
"在 GiteeAI 平台上，使用 AISBench 工具在 GSM8K 基准集上对模型进行了测试验证：在 7cd45e "
"版本配置下，模型在精度生成模式下达到了 94.77% 的准确率。"

msgid "The markdown formatted result is as follows:"
msgstr "Markdown 格式的结果如下："

msgid ""
"| dataset | version | metric | mode | vllm-api-general-chat |\n"
"| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |\n"
"| gsm8k | 7cd45e | accuracy | gen | 94.77 |"
msgstr ""
"| dataset | version | metric | mode | vllm-api-general-chat |\n"
"| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |\n"
"| gsm8k | 7cd45e | accuracy | gen | 94.77 |"

msgid "## Performance"
msgstr "## 性能"

msgid "### Using AISBench"
msgstr "### 使用 AISBench"

msgid "### Using vLLM Benchmark"
msgstr "### 使用 vLLM Benchmark"

msgid "Run performance evaluation of `Hunyuan-A13B-Instruct` as an example."
msgstr "以 `Hunyuan-A13B-Instruct` 为例运行性能评估。"

msgid ""
"Refer to [vllm benchmark](https://docs.vllm.ai/en/latest/benchmarking/) for "
"more details."
msgstr ""
"更多详情请参考 [vllm benchmark](https://docs.vllm.ai/en/latest/benchmarking/)。"

msgid "There are three `vllm bench` subcommands:"
msgstr "`vllm bench` 包含三个子命令："

msgid ""
"- `latency`: Benchmark the latency of a single batch of requests.\n"
"- `serve`: Benchmark the online serving throughput.\n"
"- `throughput`: Benchmark offline inference throughput."
msgstr ""
"- `latency`：对单批次请求的延迟进行基准测试。\n"
"- `serve`：对在线服务吞吐量进行基准测试。\n"
"- `throughput`：对离线推理吞吐量进行基准测试。"

msgid "Take the `serve` as an example. Run the code as follows."
msgstr "以 `serve` 为例，运行如下代码。"

msgid ""
"After about several minutes, you can get the performance evaluation result."
msgstr "大约几分钟后，即可获得性能评估结果。"

msgid "output:"
msgstr "输出："
